    "title": "Mango with Sweet Fish Sauce",
    "content": "Mangoes are a staple fruit for Thais, used in both savory and sweet dishes. The sweet fish sauce lies in a realm of both sweet and savory, with caramel notes from palm sugar and briny notes from various types of dried shrimp to serve as an appetizer with sour green mangoes.",
