    "title": "Meat Free Thai Red Curry",
    "content": "A hassle-free vegetarian curry that is full of flavor. While it is meat free, this Thai Red Curry is filled with juicy protein pieces from Quorn to satisfy your belly. Simply pan fry the meatless pieces before mixing it into the curry to simmer and soak up the fragrant spices and rich coconut milk. The addition of diced mangoes enhances the dish by balancing out the creaminess of the curry with its bright flavors. Best eaten with rice and a healthy serving of broccoli. ",
