    "content": "A gorgeous salad is a welcome treat on a hot day. The citrus and fresh herbs in this Thai Style Citrus Salmon Salad offer refreshing textures, which are juxtaposed against the richness of the salmon and the spiciness of the sauce. Whether you serve it as a side dish or enjoy it as a main, the bright notes and colors of this beautiful dish won\u2019t fail to delight!",
