    "content": "Nothing like roast chicken to brighten up any festive occasion. Impress your loved ones with my Firecracker Chicken, which comes with a twist that includes explosive flavors on top of the most tender and juicy roast chicken. Drizzled with a fragrant Firecracker Butter sauce made out of butter, tamarind and just enough spice, this chicken dish is guaranteed to excite your taste buds with its unique yet delicious combination of flavors. If that's not enough to make you merry, this recipe is also suitable for those who are on a keto diet.",
