        "1\u00bd tbsp belacan (shrimp paste)",
        "3 red chilies (seeded)",
        "7 shallots (peeled, alternative: 1 medium onion)",
        "3 cloves garlic (peeled)",
        "2 tbsp vegetable oil",
        "salt (to taste)"
