    "title": "Sweet Potato Fries",
    "content": "Sweet, salty and extremely addictive, our version of Sweet Potato Fries works marvelously as a side dish to your dinner roast or burger or as an afternoon snack. What\u2019s more, you probably already have the key ingredients in your kitchen \u2013salt, oil, garlic powder and pepper! Undemanding and requiring little post-cooking cleaning (if you choose to have it baked), this crispy and healthy dish will keep you coming back for more.",
