        "1 medium size potato (sliced into \u00bc inch thickness)",
        "1 carrot (cut into 1 inch slice)",
        "1 eggplant (cut into large cubes)",
        "1 zucchini (cut into large cubes)",
        "2 tomatoes (large diced)",
