    "content": "This delicious vegan plate of seared mushrooms with a cucumber and tomato ragout is like a hug on a plate \u2013 healthy, hearty and warm with Mediterranean herbs and spices. The wonderful umami flavors of mushroom intensifies when seared, leaving a slightly charred exterior and an absolutely juicy interior. You\u2019ll definitely have no problem polishing off this addictive snack, especially when paired with a refreshing and creamy Burnt Cucumber Saksuka!",
