        "5 shallots",
        "6 chili padi (bird\u2019s eye chili)",
        "1 tbsp curry powder",
        "1 tbsp oyster sauce",
        "1 tbsp soy sauce",
        "1 tsp cooking caramel (substitute with 1 tsp kecap manis)"
