    "content": "You don't need to wait for 4th of July to sink your teeth into this juicy, crispy, classic American Cheese Bacon Burger. Each bite is bursting with sweet and savory flavours - the crusty toasted buns give way to the fresh crunch of onion and tomatoes, followed by oozing cheese over the fatty minced beef that's grilled to perfection. Any day can be a cheat day with this intensely rich food experience.",
