    "content": "Kimchi Grilled Cheese is an interesting twist on the much-loved grilled cheese sandwich. The spicy and sour kimchi is surprisingly, a perfect complement to cheese. Easy enough make for lunch or dinner, this sandwich brings a delightful adventure to your everyday dining experience.",
