    "title": "One-Pot Kimchi Pumpkin Mac and Cheese",
    "content": "Heard of Mac and Cheese, what about Kimchi Pumpkin Mac and Cheese?  This dish is suitable for those who find the Classic Mac and Cheese too cheezy as the addition of Kimchi and Pumpkin gives this Classic Western dish a Korean twist. To make things easier, this recipe only requires one pot and two steps. Yes, that simple!  Time to make your own Mac and Cheese at home!",
