    "title": "Mushroom and Tempeh Rendang",
    "content": "\"Love the luscious, creamy rendang but can\u2019t have meat? We\u2019ve got you covered with our special Mushroom and Tempeh Rendang that packs the same punch while staying meatless! Mushrooms and Tempeh make for great vegetarian rendang ingredients due to their textures \u2013 slightly chewy and soft but not mushy when cooked. This wonderful rendang is spicy, sweet and tangy all at once. Serve it up with a steaming plate of basmati rice and you are all set. ",
