    "title": "ROASTED HOISIN CHICKEN ",
    "content": "Hoisin sauce is a popular Chinese condiment made from fermented soybean paste and seasonings such as garlic, chili peppers and sesame. In this dish, we combine basic pantry condiments and roast the chicken using hoisin to sweeten the dish. \r\n\r\n",
