        "(peeled & cut into chunks)",
        "2 whole potatoes\u00a0",
        "(peeled & cut into chunks)",
        "2 whole tomatoes\u00a0",
        "(wedges)",
        "1 large onion\u00a0",
        "(peeled & cut into wedges)",
