        "2 zucchinis (made into zoodles)",
        "2 + 1 tbsp Seriously Keto Teriyaki Sauce",
        "2 tbsp Ghee (or oil of choice)",
        "1 clove garlic (finely minced)",
        "4 slices ginger",
