    "content": "When a good Filipino friend of mine asked me to try adobo my first thought was it\u2019s just a stew. Each country has their own version of traditional stew, so I decided to give it a try \u2013and I was impressed. The complexity of the flavours in adobo was intriguing. It has a pleasant tinge of sour that is very distinct. I was sold. ",
