        "2 tbsp fresh coriander (chopped)",
        "1 tbsp\u00a0(sesame oil)",
        "1 tbsp vegetable oil\u00a0",
        "4 tbsp soya sauce\u00a0",
        "\u00bc tsp salt",
        "\u00bc tsp black pepper",
        "square spring rolls sheets\u00a0",
        "cornstarch and water for sealing the rolls",
        "oil (for frying)"
