    "content": "Blushed juicy plums are the stand-out star in this stir-fry triple mushroom dish. Flavoured with garlic and onions, a fistful of red plums, blistered till jammy-soft, adds fruity sweetness to a sizzling vegetarian pot that\u2019s oozing with umami juices from oyster, button and shitake mushrooms. Best eaten with rice on a lazy weekend. ",
