    "title": "Vegetarian Poon Choi",
    "content": "An auspicious dish that is rooted in tradition, Poon Choi is a must have for any Chinese New Year family gathering. This year, my family has decided to be more sustainable and a little lighter on the stomach during the festivities, so I found joy in adding a modern twist to this classic dish by creating my Vegetarian Poon Choi. Filled with over 16 different mushrooms, vegetables and meat free proteins, this veggie delight makes for an equally delicious and filling yet healthy meal. ",
    "image_url": "https://asianfoodnetwork.com/content/dam/afn/global/en/recipes/vegetarian-poon-choi/AFN_vegetarian_poon_choi_main_image_host.jpg.transform/recipestep-img/img.jpg",
