                "Cut the king oyster mushroom into big slices, about 0.5cm thick.",
                "Turn off the heat and soak all the dried/canned mushrooms (lion\u2019s mane, Shiitake and abalone mushroom) to remove any impurities, for at least 15 minutes or until they have softened.",
