    "content": "Just like the famous Kung Pao chicken, this Stir-Fried Chicken and Cashews in Honey Soy is really easy to whip up on busy weekdays. It offers a crunchy, savory treat that pairs well with many different sides. High in protein, fibre and vitamins, this flavorful low-carb dish boasts of great textures with moist chicken and crunchy roasted cashews and will definitely be one of the dishes you won\u2019t hesitate to cook again.",
