    "title": "Taiwanese Tea Egg",
    "content": "Infused with the flavors of salty soy sauce and black tea, Taiwanese Tea Eggs achieve a rare combination of health, flavor, and convenience. And they are so easy to make. Enjoy this as a snack or an accompaniment to any meal.",
