    "title": "Es Goyobod",
    "content": "A refreshingly cool Indonesian dessert, Es Goyobod typically consists of shaved ice with a coconut milk base, a mix of various jellies, fruits and coconut slices, topped with sticky sweet syrup. Unique to this dessert is the cubed hunkwe jelly, made from mung bean starch. Best served on a scorching hot day, it\u2019s also commonly served during Ramadan in West Java.",
