    "content": "A favorite of many, sosis bakar or grilled sausage is a simple yet delicious snack. Commonly sold by cart vendors with their makeshift grilling pan, the snack is known for their spiral carvings that tempt kids and adults alike. Dipped into a special sauce for its signature caramelized glaze, it is best served with mayonnaise and chili sauce.",
