    "content": "Ayam Lodho is a delicious chicken dish from Tulungagung in Indonesia. This Javanese specialty is prepared by first, roasting the chicken till its crispy golden brown on the outside, and tender and juicy on the inside. It is then cooked in a spicy coconut broth - perfect for those who enjoy some heat in their food. Enjoy it with a bowl of rice for a wholesome weeknight dinner. ",
