    "title": "Ayam Suwir Pedas Kemangi",
    "content": "Spice lovers rejoice! Here\u2019s an Indonesian dish with a delightfully spicy kick. Simply prepared by cooking shredded chicken with a combination of chili, spices and basil, Ayam Suwir Pedas Kemangi can be enjoyed with rice, bread or even lettuce wraps for a low carb meal. ",
