    "title": "Grontol Jagung (Steamed Corn Kernels with Coconut)",
    "content": "Grontol Jagung is a popular Indonesian street snack that is commonly found in Central Java. Dried corn kernels are boiled before they are sprinkled with a grated coconut mixture that has been steamed and flavored with pandan leaves. ",
