    "title": "Nasi Goreng Gila",
    "content": "While Nasi Goreng Gila is made with the same spices as regular fried rice, this popular Indonesian variation contains an additional mix of delicious ingredients that can drive you - as its name suggests - 'crazy'. It\u2019s rarely found outside Jakarta, so if you crave this hearty, mouthwatering dish with a spicy kick, we\u2019ve got your back with this simple recipe. ",
