    "title": "Perkedel Tahu",
    "content": "Perkedel, or Frikadel, is a fried Indonesian snack that is usually made from potatoes and minced meat. For this Perkedel Tahu recipe, white tofu is used as the main ingredient instead. Seasoned with leeks, chicken powder and white pepper, the tofu is shaped into bite-sized patties before being fried. ",
