        "4 red shallots",
        "1 piece of garlic",
        "6 bird\u2019s eye chilis\u00a0",
        "1 tbsp of Indonesian sweet soya sauce / oyster sauce (optional)",
        "\u00bd tsp sesame oil (optional)",
        "pinch of salt and sugar",
