    "title": "Nasi Goreng Pete (Stink Bean Fried Rice)",
    "content": "Nasi Goreng Pete is an Indonesian favorite! This variation of fried rice includes spices such as sweet soy sauce, shallots, garlic and spices. However it is the secret ingredient, pete or petai (stinky bean), that makes this dish a firm favorite for petai lovers be it for lunch or dinner, or both!",
