                "Add white rice then stir until the ingredients coat the rice evenly.\u00a0",
                "Add the rest of the seasoning and stir.",
                "Add butter and coat rice evenly.\u00a0",
                "Refrigerated leftover rice makes the best fried rice.",
                "\u00a0"
