    "title": "Cumi Judes",
    "content": "A seafood dish from Indonesia, Cumi Judes is known for its extremely spicy nature. Made with salted squid cooked in a unique blend of chili, shallots, garlic, lemongrass, chicken powder and lime leaves, it is packed with loads of flavor to excite your taste buds. Have a cool dessert on standby to offset the heat after the meal!",
