    "title": "Dendeng Ragi",
    "content": "Dendeng Ragi is an Indonesian beef jerky that is cooked with grated coconut. A simple and flavorful dish that\u2019s set to entice your appetite, it is a staple for lunch or dinner in every East Javanese household. Enjoy the savory, sweet and aromatic flavors with a plate of warm rice and homemade sambal. Since it is dried, it's easy to store and reheat for later days.",
