    "title": "Es Lontrong Slawi     ",
    "content": "Es Lontrong Slawi is a sweet Indonesian dessert which originated from the streets of Slawi in Central Java. This local delicacy is typically made out of a refreshing blend of shaved ice, grass jelly, green beans, white bread, coconut milk, red syrup and kolang kaling (also known as attap chee or sugar palm fruit). Filled with an exciting mix of toppings with different textures, this sweet and creamy treat is a delight to have, especially on a hot day. ",
