    "content": "Looking for a vegan dinner that\u2019s both simple and affordable? Sate Tempe is the dish for you. Skewered tempe (fermented soybeans) seasoned with sweet soy sauce and spices like chili, ginger and turmeric, this simple dish usually has a delicious smoky flavor as it is grilled over burning hot coal. With its browned, caramelized appearance and its sweet and savory taste, you\u2019ll find that this meat-free version is just as delicious as the usual sate. Skip the chicken powder and this Indonesian dish is fully vegan-friendly.",
