    "content": "Tahu Gimbal Saus Kacang is a dish that can be commonly found in Semarang, Indonesia. It consists of fried tofu, tempeh and shrimp, paired with an assortment of crunchy vegetables. Served with a savory peanut sauce, this tasty meal is perfect for a light midweek lunch. ",
