    "title": "Stick Kentang Keju (Potato Cheese Sticks)",
    "content": "Stick Kentang Keju is a quick and easy snack to make. As the name implies, these cheesy potato sticks are made from a blend of steamed potatoes and cheddar cheese. Deep fried to golden brown perfection, these bite-sized treats are addictively savory and crunchy. Perfect to munch on when you are having a movie marathon!",
