    "content": "Pontianak Iced Aloe Vera is a refreshing drink made with aloe vera, which is widely grown in Pontianak, Kalimantan. The hot climate makes it suitable for this plant to thrive. This fresh and cooling drink is much-loved by many, especially on hot and sunny days.",
