    "title": "Lele Bakar (Grilled Catfish)",
    "content": "Lele Bakar, or grilled catfish has low calories and is packed with lean protein, and healthy fats. To cook Lele Bakar, the fish is beautifully marinated with coriander, turmeric, garlic and lime juice giving it its complex flavours of spicy, sourish, salty, and sweetish. Delicious and light enough to have seconds and possibly third servings! ",
