    "title": "Buncis Telur Asin (Salted Egg Green Bean)",
    "content": "Buncis Telur Asin is a unique and delicious way of cooking green beans as it combines the crunchy beans with the mouth watering flavors of salted egg yolk. Perfectly salty and spicy, this is a tasty way for daily intake of fibers and vegetables.",
    "image_url": "https://asianfoodnetwork.com/content/dam/afn/global/en/recipes/buncis-telur-asin-salted-egg-green-bean/BUNCIS_TELUR_ASIN_Article_1920x1280_4.jpg.transform/recipestep-img/img.jpg",
