    "title": "Otak Otak Ikan Goreng (Fried Fish Cake)",
    "content": "Otak Otak Ikan Goreng is a favorite snack of school kids, particularly those living along the coast or seafront. A nutritious and relatively easy dish to make, using mackerel as a main ingredient and tapioca flour and coconut milk to enhance the taste, it is an option for a midday hunger stopper.",
