    "title": "Pancake Nangka Gula Jawa (Jackfruit Pancake with Palm Sugar Syrup)",
    "content": "Pancake Nangka Gula Jawa is a great dish for iftar, which is the breaking of fast. It can also be eaten for breakfast, or as a snack. This jackfruit pancake with Javanese melted palm sugar sauce provides adequate carbs and sugar, perfect for a boost of sweetness. Palm sugar isn\u2019t as sweet as white sugar, it is balanced to go along with the pancakes.",
