    "title": "Ayam Tangkap",
    "content": "Ayam Tangkap is an iconic dish from Aceh that is well-loved by locals. Fried chicken seasoned in aromatic herbs and spices, this Indonesian delight is truly unique as it is served with fried pandan, curry leaves, and green chilies. These crispy additions elevate the dish with extra flavor, texture and fragrance. A vibrant meal to brighten up any dinner table!   ",
