    "content": "Bugis Grilled Banana is a snack of the Bugis and Makassar people of South Sulawesi. Using pisang raja, considered the King of bananas with its unique taste, this Pisang Bakar Bugis is both a comfort food and a healthy snack. Commonly sold by vendors, some come with a sprinkling of cheese.",
