        "4 eggs",
        "\u00bc cup unsweetened almond milk (room temperature)",
        "\u215b tsp xanthan gum (optional)",
        "\u00bd tsp salt",
        "1 tsp swerve",
        "ghee",
        "For Bamboo Shoots :",
        "1 pack bamboo shoots",
        "2 tbsp Janti\u2019s Keto Teriyaki Sauce",
        "3 cloves garlic (minced)",
