                "In the same pan add in the cloves, star anise, cinnamon stick and fry for 1 minute before adding the blended items and continue to fry until fragrant the onion paste become slightly brown. Now add in the masala spice, turmeric, coriander powder, chili powder and fry until fragrant.\u00a0",
