    "title": "Chicken Katsudon",
    "content": "The Katsudon is one of the most well-known Japanese rice bowls in the world, and it is easy to see why \u2013it is the perfect balance between sweet and salty, filled with delightful textures, thanks to the crunchy fried chicken and fat grains of rice swimming in a creamy sea of egg. To fully enjoy this dish, eat it hot off the stove!",
