    "title": "Green Bean Water",
    "content": "Green Bean Water is literally, the coolest thing on the block. Boiled under medium heat, it\u2019s incredibly light, mood lifting, and used as an everyday tonic in Traditional Chinese Medicine. Fans of the magical brew believe that the make-in-15mins green beans, or mung beans, help clear heat and toxins from the body, improving circulation in the process. Now isn\u2019t that\u2019s so much good for so little effort? ",
