    "title": "Soothingly Warm Luo Han Guo Tea",
    "content": "A warming sweet fruit drink famously used to calm irritated throats and other respiratory annoyances. It\u2019s easy to make too, in 10 mins, you crack and break the monk fruit drink into smaller pieces, then boil it with a comforting blend of honey dates, apricot kernels (north and south almond) and sweet dried figs. Too sweet for your liking? Use less monk fruit, for its 200 times sweeter than sugar. ",
