    "content": "The secret to a perfect McGriddles pancake bun is a golden cup of maple syrup. You see, the floral sweetness of maple melting into doughy bun batter is the thing that makes this cult breakfast burger so loved. But that\u2019s not complete though, you\u2019ll need to whip up (very easily), the egg and sausage patty combo for the inside.  ",
