    "content": "Blondies are rich, dense dessert bars designed to be indulged in on their own. Here, we add in flavorful, pungent Musang King durians for a whole new level of blondie goodness. Baking the bittersweet Mao Shan Wang gives it a mellower, deeper flavor, giving you and your loved ones a new way to enjoy the durian.These bars are super easy to store due to their compact nature \u2013that is if any is left after you\u2019ve made them!",
