    "title": "Getuk Singkong",
    "content": "Getuk Singkong is a sweet Indonesian snack that is commonly found in Central and East Java. Mainly made of cassava and palm sugar, it is also sprinkled with steamed grated coconut. Enjoy it for afternoon tea or as dessert after a satisfying meal.",
    "image_url": "https://asianfoodnetwork.com/content/dam/afn/global/en/recipes/getuk-singkong/AFN_getuk_singkong_main_image.jpg.transform/recipestep-img/img.jpg",
