    "title": "Gising Gising (Chicken & Green Beans in Coconut Milk)",
    "content": "Gising Gising literally translates to \u2018wake up, wake up\u2019 and with a delicious combination of cream and spice, this Filipino dish will definitely perk you up with its well-balanced flavors. While it is traditionally made with winged beans, this recipe uses green beans as a substitute as it offers similar taste and texture. The addition of ground chicken makes it the perfect dish to serve with rice for a wholesome meal.",
    "image_url": "https://asianfoodnetwork.com/content/dam/afn/global/en/recipes/gising-gising/AFN_gising_gising_main_image.jpg.transform/recipestep-img/img.jpg",
